00:00:02.604 --> 00:00:03.638 position:21% line:89% align:start
[singing in Japanese]

00:01:11.706 --> 00:01:12.540 position:21% line:89% align:start
[singing in Japanese]

00:01:25.285 --> 00:01:27.321 position:30% line:83% align:start
[narrator] Life
on a deserted island

00:01:27.354 --> 00:01:30.558 position:10% line:83% align:start
had done little to cure Nadia
of her selfish ways.

00:01:30.592 --> 00:01:33.561 position:16% line:83% align:start
In fact, things have only
taken a turn for the worse.

00:01:33.595 --> 00:01:36.196 position:24% line:83% align:start
Early one morning,
she dragged Jean, Marie,

00:01:36.229 --> 00:01:38.600 position:35% line:83% align:start
and King on
a march to the jungle,

00:01:38.633 --> 00:01:41.502 position:38% line:83% align:start
renaming
everything to suit her taste.

00:01:41.536 --> 00:01:44.271 position:30% line:83% align:start
She proclaimed
that she was a new girl now

00:01:44.304 --> 00:01:47.542 position:10% line:83% align:start
and would no longer need the
help of science or technology

00:01:47.575 --> 00:01:49.577 position:16% line:89% align:start
to live her simple life.

00:01:49.611 --> 00:01:51.846 position:38% line:83% align:start
However,
her rebirth did not stop her

00:01:51.879 --> 00:01:54.448 position:7% line:83% align:start
from raiding her friends' camp
for supplies

00:01:54.481 --> 00:01:57.685 position:7% line:83% align:start
and draining their food stores
for her own needs.

00:01:58.686 --> 00:02:01.689 position:10% line:83% align:start
She soon discovered that life
without scientific progress

00:02:01.723 --> 00:02:05.492 position:16% line:83% align:start
was a bit more difficult
than she had assumed.

00:02:05.526 --> 00:02:08.763 position:16% line:83% align:start
Jean and Marie generously
took her back to live with them.

00:02:08.796 --> 00:02:13.701 position:10% line:83% align:start
But will her explosive nature
lead to further problems?

00:02:13.735 --> 00:02:15.803 position:19% line:89% align:start
What will happen next?

00:02:18.205 --> 00:02:18.873 position:44% line:89% align:start
[pop]

00:02:20.608 --> 00:02:22.610 position:27% line:89% align:start
[birds chirping]

00:02:22.644 --> 00:02:24.478 position:27% line:89% align:start
[waves crashing]

00:02:26.914 --> 00:02:28.716 position:7% line:89% align:start
How dare you use meat in this?

00:02:28.750 --> 00:02:30.417 position:19% line:89% align:start
How do you know I did?

00:02:30.450 --> 00:02:32.386 position:27% line:83% align:start
How can you be so
contemptuous of me?

00:02:32.419 --> 00:02:34.321 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'd like to know
how you could tell it was there.

00:02:34.354 --> 00:02:37.224 position:27% line:83% align:start
Jean, I can tell
when I'm tasting it.

00:02:37.257 --> 00:02:38.559 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's yummy.

00:02:38.593 --> 00:02:40.928 position:13% line:83% align:start
I don't have a problem with
the taste,

00:02:40.962 --> 00:02:42.797 position:10% line:89% align:start
just that you used it at all.

00:02:42.830 --> 00:02:45.332 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well, we really don't have
a whole lot of food

00:02:45.365 --> 00:02:47.267 position:30% line:83% align:start
to choose from
around here, Nadia.

00:02:47.300 --> 00:02:49.269 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, please. Listen.

00:02:49.302 --> 00:02:52.272 position:30% line:83% align:start
-It's no meat!
-[sighs] Right.

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:54.776 position:16% line:89% align:start
Eating animals is cruel!

00:02:54.809 --> 00:02:57.310 position:24% line:83% align:start
No human being has
the right to feed off others!

00:02:57.344 --> 00:02:59.246 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's not an animal!

00:02:59.279 --> 00:03:00.648 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's food for us to eat.

00:03:01.949 --> 00:03:04.786 position:7% line:83% align:start
The worst thing is that you hid
it in there just to trick me.

00:03:04.819 --> 00:03:06.688 position:19% line:89% align:start
Why did you lie to me?

00:03:06.721 --> 00:03:08.656 position:16% line:89% align:start
But I didn't lie to you.

00:03:08.690 --> 00:03:10.625 position:19% line:83% align:start
And besides, it's very
nutritious

00:03:10.658 --> 00:03:12.627 position:24% line:83% align:start
and good to keep up
your strength.

00:03:12.660 --> 00:03:14.629 position:19% line:83% align:start
No creature should have
to give up its life

00:03:14.662 --> 00:03:16.631 position:30% line:83% align:start
so that you can
build up your strength.

00:03:16.664 --> 00:03:17.999 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh, I see.

00:03:18.032 --> 00:03:19.967 position:21% line:83% align:start
Then why don't you go
and tell that to all the animals

00:03:20.001 --> 00:03:21.736 position:7% line:89% align:start
that eat each other to survive?

00:03:21.769 --> 00:03:23.236 position:16% line:89% align:start
That's another sick lie!

00:03:23.270 --> 00:03:25.338 position:21% line:83% align:start
It's a scientifically
proved fact

00:03:25.372 --> 00:03:27.474 position:27% line:83% align:start
that some animals
eat each other to live.

00:03:27.508 --> 00:03:29.644 position:16% line:83% align:start
And that's why I can give
no credence

00:03:29.677 --> 00:03:30.978 position:13% line:89% align:start
to your deceptive science.

00:03:31.012 --> 00:03:33.715 position:35% line:83% align:start
Everything
it teaches is a big lie!

00:03:33.748 --> 00:03:35.917 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're a liar! Ugh!

00:03:35.950 --> 00:03:38.519 position:16% line:83% align:start
Man has been eating meat
since the dawn of time

00:03:38.553 --> 00:03:40.353 position:5% line:89% align:start
and that is why he's multiplied.

00:03:41.756 --> 00:03:43.323 position:10% line:89% align:start
And that's why he's so evil.

00:03:43.356 --> 00:03:45.325 position:30% line:89% align:start
What? Nonsense!

00:03:45.358 --> 00:03:47.327 position:30% line:83% align:start
Maybe you don't
want to admit it, Jean.

00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:49.296 position:7% line:89% align:start
But eating meat makes you evil.

00:03:49.329 --> 00:03:50.531 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh, please.

00:03:50.565 --> 00:03:52.867 position:27% line:83% align:start
If you eat that,
you'll be as evil as Jean is.

00:03:52.900 --> 00:03:54.836 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Did you know that?
-[grunts]

00:03:54.869 --> 00:03:56.537 position:10% line:89% align:start
You should throw it all away.

00:03:56.571 --> 00:03:58.472 position:13% line:89% align:start
That will be such a waste.

00:03:58.506 --> 00:04:00.641 position:27% line:83% align:start
You are the ones
who are wasting everything.

00:04:00.675 --> 00:04:03.044 position:24% line:83% align:start
You waste lives so
you can fill up your stomachs!

00:04:03.077 --> 00:04:05.646 position:19% line:83% align:start
You waste your own life
if you starve to death!

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:07.347 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's better than killing.

00:04:07.380 --> 00:04:09.684 position:5% line:83% align:start
But eating meat makes your blood
strong and helps you fight off

00:04:09.717 --> 00:04:11.819 position:7% line:89% align:start
all sorts of terrible diseases.

00:04:12.687 --> 00:04:15.355 position:16% line:83% align:start
If my blood can't get by
without meat, then so be it.

00:04:15.388 --> 00:04:16.824 position:16% line:89% align:start
It still makes you evil.

00:04:16.858 --> 00:04:18.893 position:41% line:83% align:start
That is
complete nonsense, Nadia.

00:04:18.926 --> 00:04:19.827 position:21% line:89% align:start
Look at Marie and me.

00:04:19.861 --> 00:04:21.596 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ha!

00:04:21.629 --> 00:04:22.997 position:24% line:83% align:start
You lied to me, and
that proves that you're evil!

00:04:24.065 --> 00:04:25.700 position:27% line:83% align:start
Do you want to
be evil like Jean?

00:04:25.733 --> 00:04:27.367 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-How can you stand there

00:04:27.400 --> 00:04:29.003 position:19% line:89% align:start
and say that about me?

00:04:29.036 --> 00:04:31.438 position:16% line:83% align:start
And after everything that
we have been through together.

00:04:31.471 --> 00:04:33.007 position:19% line:83% align:start
And using your devious
corrupted mind,

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:34.742 position:10% line:89% align:start
you tried to make me like you

00:04:34.776 --> 00:04:36.476 position:7% line:89% align:start
by sneaking meat into my food.

00:04:36.511 --> 00:04:38.679 position:27% line:83% align:start
All I want is for
you to be healthy.

00:04:38.713 --> 00:04:41.414 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well, I won't reduce myself
to eating your sickening omelet.

00:04:42.083 --> 00:04:43.483 position:5% line:89% align:start
If you want to cook for me,

00:04:43.518 --> 00:04:44.919 position:16% line:83% align:start
you'll just have to make
a plain omelet.

00:04:45.787 --> 00:04:47.320 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:47.354 --> 00:04:48.388 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:48.421 --> 00:04:50.024 position:30% line:83% align:start
You think it's
sickening? [sighs]

00:04:52.459 --> 00:04:54.529 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hold it right there!

00:04:54.562 --> 00:04:55.863 position:30% line:89% align:start
[pan sizzling]

00:04:55.897 --> 00:04:56.964 position:30% line:89% align:start
[egg cracking]

00:04:56.998 --> 00:04:58.032 position:30% line:89% align:start
[egg sizzling]

00:04:59.567 --> 00:05:00.902 position:27% line:89% align:start
[rooster crowing]

00:05:03.538 --> 00:05:05.438 position:27% line:89% align:start
That's so funny.

00:05:05.472 --> 00:05:07.340 position:35% line:83% align:start
You have no
problem with eating an egg?

00:05:07.374 --> 00:05:08.509 position:47% line:89% align:start
No.

00:05:08.543 --> 00:05:10.545 position:7% line:83% align:start
And you know that eggs are laid
by a hen,

00:05:10.578 --> 00:05:11.779 position:13% line:89% align:start
you agree with that, right?

00:05:11.813 --> 00:05:13.446 position:33% line:89% align:start
I suppose so.

00:05:13.480 --> 00:05:15.917 position:30% line:83% align:start
An egg is just
a baby animal, Nadia!

00:05:15.950 --> 00:05:18.519 position:19% line:83% align:start
An egg is not an animal
until it's hatched, Jean.

00:05:18.553 --> 00:05:19.787 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:05:19.821 --> 00:05:21.388 position:27% line:89% align:start
[birds chirping]

00:05:21.421 --> 00:05:23.456 position:38% line:83% align:start
I'll eat
her omelet if she won't.

00:05:23.490 --> 00:05:25.593 position:10% line:89% align:start
No, this is Nadia's breakfast

00:05:25.626 --> 00:05:27.595 position:19% line:83% align:start
and she's the only one
who will eat it, okay?

00:05:27.628 --> 00:05:29.564 position:10% line:83% align:start
-Oh, she's not gonna eat it.
-I won't eat it!

00:05:29.597 --> 00:05:31.032 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm not gonna eat ever again!

00:05:31.065 --> 00:05:32.733 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh, is that so?

00:05:32.767 --> 00:05:34.101 position:19% line:89% align:start
You won't eat anything?

00:05:34.135 --> 00:05:37.638 position:16% line:83% align:start
That's what I said. I'll
show you both how to survive.

00:05:37.672 --> 00:05:40.608 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm going to live for a week
without food or water.

00:05:40.641 --> 00:05:41.909 position:16% line:89% align:start
So no water either, huh?

00:05:41.943 --> 00:05:43.476 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Not a drop.
-Yum.

00:05:43.511 --> 00:05:44.979 position:38% line:89% align:start
[giggles]

00:05:45.012 --> 00:05:47.815 position:5% line:83% align:start
Well, you better not complain to
me when you start to get hungry.

00:05:47.849 --> 00:05:49.584 position:30% line:83% align:start
You won't hear
me complain at all.

00:05:49.617 --> 00:05:51.118 position:7% line:89% align:start
You won't hear me say anything.

00:05:51.152 --> 00:05:52.653 position:30% line:83% align:start
I can't believe
you're so stubborn

00:05:52.687 --> 00:05:54.889 position:16% line:83% align:start
that you backed yourself
into this silly plan.

00:05:54.922 --> 00:05:56.524 position:19% line:89% align:start
I didn't back into it.

00:05:56.557 --> 00:05:58.059 position:24% line:83% align:start
I said I won't eat
anything and I mean it.

00:05:58.092 --> 00:06:00.027 position:30% line:89% align:start
You just watch.

00:06:00.061 --> 00:06:01.996 position:21% line:89% align:start
[tense music playing]

00:06:13.808 --> 00:06:15.643 position:27% line:89% align:start
[King chattering]

00:06:17.745 --> 00:06:20.047 position:21% line:83% align:start
You know, you really
should've eaten something

00:06:20.081 --> 00:06:22.149 position:30% line:83% align:start
to help you get
through this heat wave.

00:06:22.183 --> 00:06:25.720 position:5% line:83% align:start
I haven't eaten for the last few
days and I'm still not hungry.

00:06:27.088 --> 00:06:28.756 position:19% line:89% align:start
Jean, can I have some?

00:06:29.757 --> 00:06:32.526 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Jean groans] There's
not much left, I'm afraid.

00:06:33.194 --> 00:06:35.129 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'm so hungry,
everything vanishes

00:06:35.162 --> 00:06:37.131 position:16% line:83% align:start
when it reaches my tummy.
[giggles]

00:06:37.164 --> 00:06:40.134 position:13% line:83% align:start
Why don't you go ahead and
take some of this, too, Nadia?

00:06:40.935 --> 00:06:42.703 position:10% line:83% align:start
Why can't you get it through
your thick skull

00:06:42.737 --> 00:06:45.072 position:27% line:83% align:start
that I'm serious
about not wanting any meat?

00:06:45.106 --> 00:06:46.674 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:06:46.707 --> 00:06:50.144 position:13% line:83% align:start
I guess eating animal flesh
makes you stupid, too.

00:06:50.177 --> 00:06:51.411 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ugh!

00:06:53.047 --> 00:06:54.447 position:41% line:89% align:start
Nadia.

00:06:54.481 --> 00:06:55.116 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm hungry.

00:06:57.952 --> 00:07:01.722 position:5% line:83% align:start
She thinks she's so superior all
because of the things she eats.

00:07:01.756 --> 00:07:04.525 position:27% line:89% align:start
[King chattering]

00:07:15.703 --> 00:07:17.104 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[can clattering]
-[coughs]

00:07:17.138 --> 00:07:18.673 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[Marie] Nadia?
-[gasps]

00:07:18.706 --> 00:07:19.807 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Marie] Hmm.

00:07:20.875 --> 00:07:24.612 position:13% line:83% align:start
It tastes good, doesn't it?
I love eating meat.

00:07:24.645 --> 00:07:26.647 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Nadia] I'll never eat
the corpse of an animal.

00:07:26.681 --> 00:07:28.950 position:27% line:89% align:start
[King chattering]

00:07:31.619 --> 00:07:33.087 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Jean] What's wrong?

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:34.822 position:5% line:89% align:start
Nothing will take my hook today.

00:07:36.857 --> 00:07:38.491 position:16% line:89% align:start
The bait must be faulty.

00:07:39.160 --> 00:07:41.762 position:27% line:83% align:start
Are there no fish
living in this ocean?

00:07:42.663 --> 00:07:43.931 position:24% line:89% align:start
That's impossible.

00:07:45.266 --> 00:07:48.468 position:38% line:89% align:start
[sobbing]

00:07:49.270 --> 00:07:52.740 position:7% line:83% align:start
We've come this far only to end
up as breakfast for the sharks.

00:07:52.773 --> 00:07:55.977 position:16% line:83% align:start
I've never done anything
to deserve this cruel ending.

00:07:56.010 --> 00:07:59.113 position:10% line:83% align:start
The last sound I'll ever hear
is Sanson snoring.

00:07:59.146 --> 00:08:02.216 position:16% line:89% align:start
Wake up and do something,

00:08:02.249 --> 00:08:04.518 position:33% line:83% align:start
you worthless
sack of [indistinct]

00:08:04.552 --> 00:08:07.221 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Oh!
-Your savior is awake now.

00:08:07.254 --> 00:08:08.756 position:7% line:89% align:start
Anyone care for shark fin soup?

00:08:08.789 --> 00:08:10.791 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gunshots]

00:08:10.825 --> 00:08:12.193 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water splashing]

00:08:13.260 --> 00:08:15.730 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Bravo!
-[chuckling]

00:08:16.897 --> 00:08:18.733 position:27% line:89% align:start
[waves crashing]

00:08:19.900 --> 00:08:21.869 position:33% line:89% align:start
[chattering]

00:08:21.902 --> 00:08:24.105 position:27% line:89% align:start
[fire crackling]

00:08:26.107 --> 00:08:27.575 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[sighs]
-Still no water?

00:08:28.309 --> 00:08:29.610 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Jean] Just one second.

00:08:34.015 --> 00:08:35.182 position:35% line:83% align:start
-All done!
-Huh?

00:08:45.126 --> 00:08:46.627 position:19% line:89% align:start
This is for you, Marie.

00:08:46.660 --> 00:08:48.896 position:19% line:89% align:start
You're so sweet to me.

00:08:48.929 --> 00:08:50.564 position:27% line:89% align:start
It's no problem.

00:08:50.598 --> 00:08:51.966 position:27% line:89% align:start
Thank you, Jean.

00:08:52.800 --> 00:08:53.968 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gulping]

00:08:55.803 --> 00:08:56.971 position:27% line:89% align:start
That was so good.

00:08:57.004 --> 00:08:59.306 position:33% line:83% align:start
You and Nadia
can drink the rest of it.

00:08:59.340 --> 00:09:01.142 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, that's all right.

00:09:01.175 --> 00:09:03.110 position:7% line:89% align:start
Don't you worry a bit about us.

00:09:03.144 --> 00:09:06.213 position:10% line:83% align:start
Well, thanks for going to so
much trouble to get me a drink.

00:09:06.247 --> 00:09:08.716 position:7% line:83% align:start
We just want you to eat better
as soon as you can.

00:09:08.749 --> 00:09:10.084 position:30% line:83% align:start
That's our duty
for the next few days, Marie.

00:09:10.117 --> 00:09:11.152 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:09:12.053 --> 00:09:13.187 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm going to go out there

00:09:13.220 --> 00:09:15.022 position:16% line:83% align:start
and catch a big fish for
tonight's dinner.

00:09:15.056 --> 00:09:16.624 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'll wait right here, darling.

00:09:16.657 --> 00:09:17.825 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh, stop it.

00:09:17.858 --> 00:09:18.993 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:09:19.026 --> 00:09:20.161 position:41% line:89% align:start
Nadia.

00:09:20.194 --> 00:09:22.029 position:7% line:89% align:start
Go ahead and go fishing today.

00:09:22.063 --> 00:09:24.865 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'll keep the water cleaning
machine at full capacity.

00:09:24.899 --> 00:09:27.134 position:33% line:83% align:start
Are you still
holding a grudge against us?

00:09:27.168 --> 00:09:28.836 position:30% line:83% align:start
No, I've gotten
over that by now.

00:09:28.869 --> 00:09:30.104 position:33% line:89% align:start
Are you sure?

00:09:30.137 --> 00:09:32.006 position:27% line:83% align:start
-What did I say?
-Really?

00:09:32.039 --> 00:09:33.274 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yes, really.

00:09:35.109 --> 00:09:36.944 position:27% line:83% align:start
If you're trying
to make me angry,

00:09:36.977 --> 00:09:38.345 position:7% line:89% align:start
you're doing a good job, Jean.

00:09:38.379 --> 00:09:39.814 position:41% line:89% align:start
Whoops.

00:09:39.847 --> 00:09:42.817 position:16% line:83% align:start
Just go get in your boat
and murder some fish.

00:09:46.387 --> 00:09:48.289 position:27% line:83% align:start
Why does she gets
so angry all the time?

00:09:50.224 --> 00:09:52.226 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hunger makes people angry.

00:09:54.795 --> 00:09:56.664 position:30% line:83% align:start
She gets angry
when she's not hungry.

00:09:58.365 --> 00:10:00.234 position:13% line:89% align:start
I can't get angry with her.

00:10:00.267 --> 00:10:02.269 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm too hungry for that.

00:10:04.839 --> 00:10:07.208 position:27% line:89% align:start
[fire crackling]

00:10:07.241 --> 00:10:09.276 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water trickling]

00:10:14.348 --> 00:10:16.350 position:13% line:89% align:start
I can't believe this heat.

00:10:20.221 --> 00:10:22.790 position:10% line:89% align:start
This takes too long. [sighs]

00:10:28.129 --> 00:10:30.898 position:19% line:83% align:start
I've waited all morning
for a few warm drops from you?

00:10:30.931 --> 00:10:32.166 position:41% line:89% align:start
Well...

00:10:32.199 --> 00:10:33.300 position:30% line:89% align:start
[water rushing]

00:10:34.902 --> 00:10:36.170 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:10:36.203 --> 00:10:37.071 position:30% line:89% align:start
[pail rattling]

00:10:37.104 --> 00:10:39.707 position:38% line:89% align:start
You! Ugh!

00:10:39.740 --> 00:10:41.775 position:38% line:89% align:start
Come on!

00:10:41.809 --> 00:10:43.144 position:24% line:89% align:start
You get back here!

00:10:44.879 --> 00:10:46.914 position:44% line:89% align:start
Whoa.

00:10:46.947 --> 00:10:47.781 position:38% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:10:49.049 --> 00:10:52.386 position:27% line:89% align:start
[laughs] Spinach.

00:10:53.454 --> 00:10:56.290 position:13% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music playing]

00:11:11.272 --> 00:11:13.374 position:13% line:89% align:start
Thanks for the food, Jean!

00:11:15.476 --> 00:11:17.978 position:16% line:89% align:start
I got all of its ink out.

00:11:18.012 --> 00:11:19.914 position:21% line:89% align:start
This is so delicious!

00:11:19.947 --> 00:11:21.215 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mm-hmm.

00:11:22.983 --> 00:11:24.385 position:33% line:83% align:start
Come and have
some of this, Nadia.

00:11:27.421 --> 00:11:29.089 position:24% line:89% align:start
No, I'm all right.

00:11:35.296 --> 00:11:39.300 position:16% line:89% align:start
â™ª The Secret Blue Water

00:11:40.267 --> 00:11:42.102 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

00:11:43.871 --> 00:11:46.840 position:27% line:89% align:start
[King chattering]

00:11:46.874 --> 00:11:49.109 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

00:11:49.143 --> 00:11:51.478 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yay! Yay! Yay!

00:11:51.513 --> 00:11:53.247 position:38% line:83% align:start
Why don't
you go collect more cans

00:11:53.280 --> 00:11:55.916 position:5% line:83% align:start
so we can catch as much rainfall
as possible, Marie?

00:11:55.950 --> 00:11:57.818 position:44% line:89% align:start
Okay!

00:11:57.851 --> 00:11:59.119 position:30% line:89% align:start
Where's Nadia?

00:11:59.153 --> 00:12:00.788 position:13% line:89% align:start
She's sleeping in the tent.

00:12:01.488 --> 00:12:04.258 position:7% line:83% align:start
There are more important things
to do today than sleep.

00:12:06.961 --> 00:12:09.096 position:35% line:83% align:start
Marie, did
you eat some of this food?

00:12:09.129 --> 00:12:11.265 position:41% line:89% align:start
Not me.

00:12:11.298 --> 00:12:14.835 position:7% line:83% align:start
I thought I threw it all away,
because it was all rotted out.

00:12:14.868 --> 00:12:16.203 position:27% line:89% align:start
Could it be King?

00:12:16.237 --> 00:12:17.539 position:27% line:89% align:start
[King chattering]

00:12:17.572 --> 00:12:20.808 position:10% line:83% align:start
But he's spending every hour
on the cliff these days.

00:12:21.875 --> 00:12:23.077 position:35% line:89% align:start
Spinaches.

00:12:24.144 --> 00:12:25.346 position:33% line:89% align:start
It was Nadia!

00:12:26.313 --> 00:12:28.282 position:21% line:89% align:start
Nadia, are you okay?

00:12:28.315 --> 00:12:30.217 position:38% line:89% align:start
I'm fine.

00:12:30.251 --> 00:12:32.820 position:7% line:83% align:start
Did you eat something that was
labeled spinaches last night?

00:12:32.853 --> 00:12:33.988 position:24% line:89% align:start
Of course I didn't.

00:12:35.089 --> 00:12:36.457 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Jean] Look at it.

00:12:36.490 --> 00:12:38.359 position:13% line:89% align:start
I don't have to look at it.

00:12:39.393 --> 00:12:40.861 position:13% line:89% align:start
No! I would never do that!

00:12:40.894 --> 00:12:43.030 position:10% line:83% align:start
I would never eat Gargoyle's
food ever!

00:12:43.063 --> 00:12:44.198 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm not that bad!

00:12:44.231 --> 00:12:45.399 position:24% line:83% align:start
You should know me
well enough

00:12:45.432 --> 00:12:46.433 position:30% line:83% align:start
to know I would
never do that, Jean.

00:12:48.035 --> 00:12:49.571 position:19% line:89% align:start
It seems strange to me

00:12:49.604 --> 00:12:52.206 position:13% line:83% align:start
since there was no one here
except us and some monkeys.

00:12:52.239 --> 00:12:54.542 position:21% line:89% align:start
[monkeys chattering]

00:12:57.311 --> 00:12:58.846 position:35% line:89% align:start
I see now.

00:12:58.879 --> 00:13:00.948 position:30% line:83% align:start
I got caught in
one of Gargoyle's traps.

00:13:00.981 --> 00:13:02.816 position:27% line:89% align:start
[engine rumbling]

00:13:04.952 --> 00:13:06.920 position:13% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music playing]

00:13:06.954 --> 00:13:11.526 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Gargoyle] My old friend, Nemo,
may you rest in peace.

00:13:11.559 --> 00:13:14.395 position:30% line:83% align:start
You remain far
below the heavens.

00:13:14.428 --> 00:13:16.397 position:21% line:89% align:start
Far out of our reach,

00:13:16.430 --> 00:13:19.199 position:19% line:89% align:start
far out of our hearts.

00:13:19.233 --> 00:13:20.868 position:27% line:89% align:start
What can you see?

00:13:20.901 --> 00:13:22.369 position:24% line:89% align:start
Your only light...

00:13:22.403 --> 00:13:24.405 position:10% line:89% align:start
[soldiers] The fires of Hell!

00:13:24.438 --> 00:13:28.576 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Gargoyle] What can you feel
when you're only feeling?

00:13:28.610 --> 00:13:30.944 position:10% line:89% align:start
[soldiers] The agony of Hell!

00:13:30.978 --> 00:13:33.947 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Gargoyle] For the acts
you committed against us,

00:13:33.981 --> 00:13:36.116 position:19% line:83% align:start
you have been consigned
to the pits of Hell.

00:13:37.284 --> 00:13:39.219 position:41% line:83% align:start
For one
who found us so unnatural,

00:13:39.253 --> 00:13:41.455 position:27% line:83% align:start
you can be proud
of your destruction.

00:13:41.488 --> 00:13:44.958 position:13% line:89% align:start
By doing so, you honor us.

00:13:44.992 --> 00:13:47.629 position:30% line:83% align:start
So I shall call
this day Nemo's Day

00:13:47.662 --> 00:13:50.097 position:35% line:83% align:start
in honor of
our newfound pleasure.

00:13:50.130 --> 00:13:51.432 position:19% line:89% align:start
[cheering and applause]

00:13:53.635 --> 00:13:56.403 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Gargoyle]
We have but one dream left,

00:13:56.437 --> 00:13:58.972 position:7% line:89% align:start
to whom does this world belong?

00:13:59.006 --> 00:14:01.475 position:16% line:89% align:start
[soldiers] Neo Atlantis!

00:14:01.509 --> 00:14:03.444 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Gargoyle] Without a doubt.

00:14:03.477 --> 00:14:06.280 position:5% line:89% align:start
Today, we begin a new operation.

00:14:07.147 --> 00:14:09.850 position:27% line:83% align:start
We shall restore
the holy fortress at long last.

00:14:10.585 --> 00:14:12.886 position:5% line:89% align:start
It will carry us to the heavens.

00:14:12.920 --> 00:14:15.456 position:27% line:83% align:start
All will know of
its terrible power,

00:14:15.489 --> 00:14:18.626 position:13% line:89% align:start
all will know the Red Noah.

00:14:18.660 --> 00:14:20.562 position:21% line:89% align:start
Once it is restored,

00:14:20.595 --> 00:14:23.497 position:19% line:83% align:start
the ignorant human race
will have no choice

00:14:23.531 --> 00:14:27.502 position:24% line:83% align:start
but to cast itself
at the feet of Neo Atlantis.

00:14:27.535 --> 00:14:29.370 position:19% line:89% align:start
[cheering and applause]

00:14:31.539 --> 00:14:34.241 position:30% line:89% align:start
[rain pouring]

00:14:34.274 --> 00:14:36.176 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gulping]

00:14:36.210 --> 00:14:38.479 position:27% line:83% align:start
That's not smart
to eat rotten food.

00:14:39.346 --> 00:14:41.649 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Nadia] It was a devious trap
set by Gargoyle.

00:14:41.683 --> 00:14:44.619 position:24% line:83% align:start
He must've planted
the poisoned spinaches cans

00:14:44.652 --> 00:14:46.253 position:24% line:89% align:start
to try to kill us.

00:14:46.286 --> 00:14:49.156 position:7% line:83% align:start
Well then, it's lucky for you,
he didn't decide to use

00:14:49.189 --> 00:14:51.593 position:19% line:83% align:start
a lethal type of poison
to try to kill you with.

00:14:51.626 --> 00:14:56.063 position:5% line:83% align:start
Just admit that you ate a rotten
food and got too hungry to stop.

00:14:56.096 --> 00:14:57.632 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're so greedy.

00:14:57.665 --> 00:15:00.934 position:7% line:83% align:start
You know, Nadia, you should've
let us share our food with you.

00:15:00.968 --> 00:15:04.204 position:10% line:83% align:start
No! I would rather suffer the
worst stomach pains in the world

00:15:04.238 --> 00:15:05.439 position:21% line:89% align:start
than to ever consume

00:15:05.472 --> 00:15:07.575 position:21% line:83% align:start
the desiccated flesh
of a living creature.

00:15:09.511 --> 00:15:11.111 position:21% line:89% align:start
She sure is stubborn.

00:15:11.145 --> 00:15:13.447 position:19% line:83% align:start
Are you having trouble
with your bowels, Nadia?

00:15:13.480 --> 00:15:15.015 position:27% line:89% align:start
You have a fever?

00:15:15.048 --> 00:15:16.283 position:33% line:89% align:start
I feel fine.

00:15:16.316 --> 00:15:17.351 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:15:18.185 --> 00:15:19.386 position:33% line:89% align:start
It's a fever.

00:15:19.420 --> 00:15:21.723 position:21% line:89% align:start
I do not get fevers!

00:15:21.756 --> 00:15:24.692 position:13% line:83% align:start
I think I might have a way
to cure that really quickly.

00:15:26.661 --> 00:15:28.563 position:13% line:89% align:start
Don't bother. I need sleep.

00:15:30.097 --> 00:15:31.566 position:30% line:83% align:start
You're going to
need a lot more than that.

00:15:35.269 --> 00:15:36.738 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Nadia sighs]

00:15:36.771 --> 00:15:39.072 position:30% line:89% align:start
[rain pouring]

00:15:39.106 --> 00:15:41.008 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Jean] You're going to need
to stay here

00:15:41.041 --> 00:15:42.242 position:19% line:89% align:start
and take care of Nadia.

00:15:42.276 --> 00:15:44.411 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Marie]
But I wanna go with you.

00:15:44.445 --> 00:15:45.580 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Jean] You can't.

00:15:45.613 --> 00:15:47.615 position:30% line:83% align:start
Nadia might eat
some more rotten food.

00:15:47.649 --> 00:15:49.349 position:10% line:89% align:start
You must keep an eye on her.

00:15:50.217 --> 00:15:52.453 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Marie]
King can keep an eye on her.

00:15:52.486 --> 00:15:54.221 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Jean] No, he can't.

00:15:54.254 --> 00:15:56.691 position:19% line:83% align:start
Besides, we don't know
what might happen in the jungle.

00:15:56.724 --> 00:15:58.292 position:19% line:89% align:start
You have to stay here.

00:15:58.325 --> 00:15:59.393 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'll see you soon.

00:15:59.426 --> 00:16:00.695 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

00:16:03.464 --> 00:16:05.700 position:19% line:89% align:start
Oh, this is so boring.

00:16:06.601 --> 00:16:08.302 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

00:16:08.335 --> 00:16:10.370 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Marie] Jean! Help me!

00:16:10.404 --> 00:16:12.406 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

00:16:12.439 --> 00:16:14.274 position:30% line:89% align:start
[King purring]

00:16:15.777 --> 00:16:18.713 position:19% line:89% align:start
Wait, please don't go.

00:16:21.381 --> 00:16:23.250 position:33% line:89% align:start
[bars clank]

00:16:23.283 --> 00:16:25.319 position:38% line:89% align:start
[sobbing]

00:16:33.828 --> 00:16:36.497 position:35% line:83% align:start
Why? Why do
you have to kill him?

00:16:37.431 --> 00:16:40.535 position:38% line:83% align:start
It is not
something I want to have to do.

00:16:40.568 --> 00:16:42.737 position:35% line:83% align:start
He has hurt
you because of his illness.

00:16:43.738 --> 00:16:47.441 position:24% line:83% align:start
But Momo is my very
best friend, Ring Master.

00:16:47.474 --> 00:16:49.777 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Ring Master] If I have to
choose between the two of you,

00:16:49.811 --> 00:16:51.646 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'll take you, Nadia.

00:16:51.679 --> 00:16:54.549 position:16% line:83% align:start
Sometimes we cannot help
what must be done.

00:16:54.582 --> 00:16:59.152 position:13% line:83% align:start
[man] With this medicine we
have, he'll die very peacefully.

00:16:59.186 --> 00:17:00.622 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's better for him this way.

00:17:01.488 --> 00:17:04.091 position:13% line:83% align:start
-[Ring Master] Come, Nadia.
-No! Please don't kill him!

00:17:04.124 --> 00:17:06.628 position:13% line:83% align:start
There's got to be something
you can do to avoid this.

00:17:06.661 --> 00:17:09.797 position:35% line:89% align:start
Momo! Momo!

00:17:09.831 --> 00:17:11.231 position:47% line:89% align:start
No!

00:17:12.634 --> 00:17:14.067 position:44% line:89% align:start
Momo.

00:17:20.742 --> 00:17:22.777 position:30% line:89% align:start
[rain pouring]

00:17:26.246 --> 00:17:29.116 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Jean] This heat wave must
have dried up all the herbs.

00:17:29.149 --> 00:17:30.250 position:44% line:89% align:start
Darn!

00:17:31.251 --> 00:17:32.787 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:17:32.820 --> 00:17:34.656 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[thunder rumbling]
-[screams]

00:17:37.190 --> 00:17:39.459 position:10% line:89% align:start
This storm is getting scary.

00:17:39.493 --> 00:17:41.261 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[Marie] Jean!
-Marie?

00:17:43.363 --> 00:17:45.165 position:41% line:83% align:start
-What?
-[Marie] Jean.

00:17:45.198 --> 00:17:47.602 position:27% line:83% align:start
I thought I told
you to stay at home.

00:17:47.635 --> 00:17:49.336 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's too dangerous
for you to be out here.

00:17:49.369 --> 00:17:51.606 position:24% line:83% align:start
I got too scared to
stay there by myself.

00:17:51.639 --> 00:17:53.240 position:10% line:89% align:start
What's there to be scared of?

00:17:55.309 --> 00:17:57.210 position:44% line:89% align:start
Jean?

00:17:57.244 --> 00:17:58.580 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:17:58.613 --> 00:18:00.414 position:24% line:89% align:start
Am I bothering you?

00:18:00.447 --> 00:18:02.449 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:18:02.482 --> 00:18:05.520 position:19% line:83% align:start
You'd rather have Nadia
along on the trip, huh?

00:18:05.553 --> 00:18:06.654 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh, Marie.

00:18:06.688 --> 00:18:08.422 position:24% line:89% align:start
Don't be so silly.

00:18:20.300 --> 00:18:22.135 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Nadia]
Will you forgive me, Master?

00:18:22.169 --> 00:18:23.203 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Ring Master] Walk!

00:18:24.639 --> 00:18:26.239 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't look down.

00:18:28.643 --> 00:18:30.745 position:33% line:89% align:start
I said walk!

00:18:30.778 --> 00:18:32.145 position:19% line:89% align:start
You good for nothing--

00:18:32.179 --> 00:18:35.182 position:24% line:83% align:start
maybe you'd prefer
cleaning the tiger cages!

00:18:35.215 --> 00:18:37.250 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[whip crack]
-[screams]

00:18:38.185 --> 00:18:38.820 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:18:40.454 --> 00:18:42.690 position:41% line:83% align:start
You did
exceptionally well today.

00:18:42.724 --> 00:18:44.358 position:10% line:89% align:start
So I'm giving you extra food.

00:18:45.392 --> 00:18:47.327 position:24% line:83% align:start
You like this kind
of food, don't you?

00:18:48.295 --> 00:18:50.665 position:21% line:83% align:start
You're afraid of me,
but you shouldn't be.

00:18:50.698 --> 00:18:53.400 position:10% line:83% align:start
You see, I scold you only to
keep you from hurting yourself.

00:18:54.434 --> 00:18:56.738 position:33% line:83% align:start
You shouldn't
take it personally, Nadia.

00:18:56.771 --> 00:18:58.906 position:33% line:83% align:start
I wouldn't do
it if I didn't like you.

00:18:58.940 --> 00:19:00.440 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:19:00.474 --> 00:19:03.176 position:35% line:89% align:start
[applause]

00:19:03.210 --> 00:19:04.746 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

00:19:04.779 --> 00:19:06.648 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Jean] This is a surprise.

00:19:06.681 --> 00:19:08.850 position:24% line:83% align:start
The island is much
larger than I expected.

00:19:08.883 --> 00:19:12.319 position:24% line:83% align:start
Marie is too afraid
to go inside there, Jean.

00:19:12.352 --> 00:19:14.522 position:27% line:83% align:start
Why are you being
such a scaredy-cat today, Marie?

00:19:16.289 --> 00:19:18.926 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm afraid of dark,
cold places like this.

00:19:18.960 --> 00:19:20.595 position:21% line:89% align:start
Just wait here, then.

00:19:20.628 --> 00:19:22.697 position:35% line:89% align:start
Let's see.

00:19:22.730 --> 00:19:23.798 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh.

00:19:25.600 --> 00:19:27.902 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't get lost, Jean.

00:19:33.440 --> 00:19:34.642 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:19:36.243 --> 00:19:39.212 position:21% line:89% align:start
[eerie music playing]

00:19:39.246 --> 00:19:40.581 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's getting darker.

00:19:40.615 --> 00:19:42.750 position:5% line:89% align:start
I won't be able to see anything.

00:19:42.784 --> 00:19:45.853 position:19% line:83% align:start
Boy, I sure wish I had
my flashlight with me. Huh?

00:19:45.887 --> 00:19:48.488 position:33% line:89% align:start
[bird cawing]

00:19:48.523 --> 00:19:51.358 position:19% line:89% align:start
[intense music playing]

00:19:53.493 --> 00:19:55.495 position:44% line:89% align:start
Jean!

00:19:55.530 --> 00:19:57.665 position:13% line:89% align:start
It finally stopped raining.

00:20:02.937 --> 00:20:05.640 position:7% line:89% align:start
Hmm, I can't find them in here.

00:20:05.673 --> 00:20:09.476 position:7% line:83% align:start
So this must be an undiscovered
strain of mushroom.

00:20:09.510 --> 00:20:11.813 position:19% line:89% align:start
[intense music playing]

00:20:11.846 --> 00:20:13.346 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:20:13.380 --> 00:20:14.782 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughter]

00:20:27.762 --> 00:20:30.330 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm getting very hungry.

00:20:30.363 --> 00:20:33.668 position:16% line:83% align:start
Why can't we just go back
to camp with Nadia and King?

00:20:33.701 --> 00:20:35.603 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Jean] Marie?

00:20:38.573 --> 00:20:42.710 position:24% line:83% align:start
They're delicious.
Come here quickly.

00:20:47.380 --> 00:20:51.018 position:27% line:83% align:start
I've never eaten
anything so delicious.

00:20:51.719 --> 00:20:53.955 position:30% line:89% align:start
[harp playing]

00:20:53.988 --> 00:20:55.857 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckling]

00:20:57.792 --> 00:21:00.628 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hooray! I am the winner!

00:21:04.599 --> 00:21:05.633 position:44% line:89% align:start
Jean?

00:21:06.634 --> 00:21:08.836 position:19% line:89% align:start
What's happened to you?

00:21:08.870 --> 00:21:10.337 position:30% line:89% align:start
[chuckles] Hmm.

00:21:13.875 --> 00:21:16.577 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well, it looks like
the main course is here.

00:21:17.645 --> 00:21:18.980 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Marie] You're scaring me.

00:21:19.013 --> 00:21:20.715 position:21% line:89% align:start
You're kind of small,

00:21:20.748 --> 00:21:23.316 position:27% line:83% align:start
but I'm ready to
sink my teeth into you.

00:21:23.350 --> 00:21:24.986 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laughs]
-[thuds]

00:21:25.019 --> 00:21:26.453 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:21:27.755 --> 00:21:30.958 position:7% line:83% align:start
You better keep your teeth away
from me, do you understand me?

00:21:30.992 --> 00:21:33.594 position:13% line:83% align:start
Oh, I always brush my teeth
after every meal.

00:21:34.629 --> 00:21:36.429 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[chuckles]
-[grunts]

00:21:38.699 --> 00:21:40.433 position:27% line:89% align:start
Just look at you.

00:21:40.467 --> 00:21:42.737 position:27% line:83% align:start
Why do you cause
me so much trouble?

00:21:42.770 --> 00:21:44.972 position:21% line:83% align:start
You're supposed to be
the one taking care of me.

00:21:45.006 --> 00:21:48.643 position:13% line:83% align:start
I swear, and if you want me
to drag you home again,

00:21:48.676 --> 00:21:50.745 position:10% line:89% align:start
you better lose a few pounds.

00:21:50.778 --> 00:21:53.080 position:7% line:89% align:start
Geez, some people eat anything.

00:21:54.414 --> 00:21:56.483 position:33% line:83% align:start
You mean this
happened while he was out

00:21:56.517 --> 00:21:59.452 position:13% line:83% align:start
looking for medicinal herbs
to help cure me?

00:21:59.486 --> 00:22:02.389 position:33% line:89% align:start
3:00, cuckoo.

00:22:02.422 --> 00:22:05.392 position:16% line:83% align:start
He told me that he wanted
to sink his teeth into me

00:22:05.425 --> 00:22:07.094 position:10% line:89% align:start
and then he tried to grab me.

00:22:07.128 --> 00:22:09.362 position:24% line:89% align:start
He did this for me?

00:22:09.396 --> 00:22:10.798 position:30% line:89% align:start
Isn't he awful?

00:22:10.832 --> 00:22:12.399 position:27% line:89% align:start
Thank you, Jean.

00:22:12.432 --> 00:22:13.668 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[sobs]
-Huh?

00:22:13.701 --> 00:22:16.103 position:33% line:83% align:start
You're a big
beetle, I'm a little ant.

00:22:16.137 --> 00:22:18.606 position:7% line:89% align:start
Oh, this is getting ridiculous!

00:22:18.639 --> 00:22:20.575 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm a little tea pot.

00:22:20.608 --> 00:22:21.642 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:22:21.676 --> 00:22:24.512 position:16% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music playing]

00:22:26.948 --> 00:22:29.684 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[Nadia] Jean?
-Is it time for dessert?

00:22:31.052 --> 00:22:33.621 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Nadia] I had
a dream while you were gone.

00:22:33.654 --> 00:22:35.556 position:35% line:83% align:start
I realized
that none of us can live alone.

00:22:35.590 --> 00:22:37.490 position:24% line:89% align:start
We need each other.

00:22:37.525 --> 00:22:40.027 position:13% line:83% align:start
I had never really thought
about us that way before,

00:22:40.061 --> 00:22:41.762 position:30% line:83% align:start
but now I know
it to be the truth.

00:22:41.796 --> 00:22:45.800 position:24% line:83% align:start
I had a dream once
about a talking sausage.

00:22:45.833 --> 00:22:48.636 position:16% line:89% align:start
For so long, I was alone.

00:22:48.669 --> 00:22:51.672 position:30% line:83% align:start
I never needed
anyone's help for anything.

00:22:51.706 --> 00:22:53.574 position:21% line:83% align:start
But I soon found out
that without other people,

00:22:53.608 --> 00:22:56.177 position:5% line:89% align:start
I was making it hard for myself.

00:22:56.210 --> 00:22:59.714 position:10% line:83% align:start
He would spend all of his day
and night digging his tunnels.

00:22:59.747 --> 00:23:02.884 position:19% line:83% align:start
Now, for the first time
I can understand

00:23:02.917 --> 00:23:04.919 position:10% line:89% align:start
all for one and one for all.

00:23:04.952 --> 00:23:06.486 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Jean groans]

00:23:06.520 --> 00:23:07.420 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Nadia]
I can allow others to help me

00:23:07.454 --> 00:23:09.590 position:35% line:83% align:start
as long as
someone is thinking about me.

00:23:10.825 --> 00:23:13.027 position:13% line:83% align:start
If someone loves you enough
to worry about you,

00:23:13.060 --> 00:23:14.695 position:5% line:89% align:start
then you have all that you need,

00:23:14.729 --> 00:23:16.564 position:16% line:89% align:start
especially if that person

00:23:16.597 --> 00:23:19.634 position:7% line:83% align:start
is willing to put their life in
danger to help you.

00:23:19.667 --> 00:23:22.503 position:35% line:83% align:start
That's what
I learned from my dream, Jean.

00:23:24.505 --> 00:23:27.541 position:35% line:83% align:start
It's a lot
heavier than I expected.

00:23:27.575 --> 00:23:30.811 position:16% line:83% align:start
I so want you to take me
to Africa with you some day.

00:23:30.845 --> 00:23:33.180 position:30% line:83% align:start
Africa is such
a big place, Nadia.

00:23:33.214 --> 00:23:35.883 position:16% line:83% align:start
Perhaps, you should stop
talking now, Jean.

00:23:37.151 --> 00:23:38.185 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:23:39.954 --> 00:23:41.789 position:19% line:89% align:start
Take your glasses off.

00:23:41.822 --> 00:23:42.823 position:44% line:89% align:start
Okay.

00:23:42.857 --> 00:23:45.059 position:27% line:89% align:start
I can't see you.

00:23:45.092 --> 00:23:48.062 position:5% line:89% align:start
Now, Jean, stay with me forever.

00:23:48.095 --> 00:23:50.131 position:30% line:89% align:start
[King purring]

00:23:55.770 --> 00:23:56.604 position:21% line:89% align:start
[singing in Japanese]

